window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ian must pull off the impossible.</b></p> <p>Achemiss is a thousand-year-old necromancer with potent shadow magic and a trove of artifacts. To save his world and honor his deal with Karanos, Ian has one task.</p> <p>Assassinate him.</p> <p>With Maria, Karanos, and the ever-charming Crystal at his side, Ian seeks out artifacts to level the playing field. He explores treacherous planes and participates in a trial run by the white faction.</p> <p>He’ll learn that the upper limit on power is far greater than he thought.</p>"; 
